*'''American Heritage Dictionary''' (via answers.com) lists all 3 spelling alternatives for the noun sense in the order: resumé, resume, résumé.
*'''Collins Word Exchange''' lists only “résumé” for the noun sense.
*'''Merriam-Webster Online''' lists all 3 spelling alternatives for the noun sense in the order: résumé, resume, resumé.
*'''MSN Encarta Dictionary''' lists all 3 spelling alternatives for the noun sense in the order: résumé, resumé, resume.
*'''Diccionario Oxford Pocket Edición Latinoamericana''' lists only “resumé” for the noun sense.

